.name
CenterScreen
.author
Stefan Sticht
.type
Display Commodity
.short
Center frontmost screen
.description
A commodity which centers the frontmost screen horizontally
on hotkey.  Useful if you normally operate with overscan
screens and an old program opens a normal size screen.
.version
1.05
.requirements
Requires at least AmigaOS 2.0
